<section class="oe_container">
   <div class="oe_row oe_spaced">
           <h2 class="oe_slogan" style="color:crimson;"><b>Base Fleet Reservation
</h2>
           <p class="oe_mt32"  style="color:olive;">
This module allow employee to request for the vehicle reservation.<br><br><b> Main Features</b><br>
    * Employee will request for vehicle.<br/>
    * It will be confirmed by employee.<br/>
    * Approve Request By the Head of Unit<br/>
    * Approved Request By the Coordinator<br/>
    * Reserved Request By the Manager and it will be create Event<br/>
    * Return info will add to the event from wizard<br/>
    * Create Invoice by the Reservation Manager<br/>
    * Send Mail to employees directly after month<br/>
    For more Details :- https://youtu.be/0UwDqGY8gPA
    <p class="oe_mt32"  style="color:olive;">
<b> Menu Items:</b><br>
    * Vehicle Reservation<br/>
    * Vehicle Reservation/Vehicle/Vehicle.<br/>
    * Vehicle Reservation/Reservations/Reservations<br/>
    * Vehicle Reservation/Configuration/Vehicle Type<br/>
    * Vehicle Reservation/Configuration/Vehicle Sub Type<br/>
   </div>
</section>
